美利堅替法國首次勝出澳洲最高獎金賽事[[墨爾本盃|墨爾本盃]]<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|author=Caryl Williamson|coauthors=|title=Americain confirms Cup as truly global|url=http://www.aapracing.com.au/news/racing/RNS-article71766-page38-encNzE3ODI6NzE3ODE6NzE3ODA6NzE3Nzk6NzE3Nzg6NzE3Nzc6NzE3NzY6NzE3Njc6NzE3NjY6NzE3NjU6|work=|publisher=[[澳聯社|澳聯社]]|date=2010-11-02|accessdate=2010-12-07}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>，是歷來首匹墨爾本盃冠軍角逐香港國際賽事的馬匹，之前所勝出的分級賽都是大長途賽事。爆冷本年在今季開始衰退，但在[[女皇盃|愛彼女皇盃]]克服了慢步速勝出賽事，更成為香港賽馬史上最高獎金的馬匹<ref name="AbleOne VivaPataca">{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 大摩 Encore G1孖寶 |url= http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20100426/rjnewa0001x0.html |work=  |publisher= Daily Sports |date= 2010-04-26 |accessdate= 2010-12-07 |archive-date= 2016-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011046/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20100426/rjnewa0001x0.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。網絡電郵連續第三年參戰香港瓶，在去年回到日本持續好表現，終於今年5月勝出第一個分級賽冠軍[[春季天皇賞|春季天皇賞]]<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 目覚めたジャガー |url= http://www.daily.co.jp/horse/schedule2010/100503g1.shtml |work=  |publisher= Daily Sports |date= 2010-05-02 |accessdate= 2010-12-07 |archive-date= 2017-01-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170112141727/http://www.daily.co.jp/horse/schedule2010/100503g1.shtml |dead-url= no }}</ref>。至勁寶在今年勝出意大利重要的長途賽事[[米蘭大賽|米蘭大賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Lo show dei campioni: così l’ippica risponde in pista a accuse ingiustificate |url= http://www.ilgiornale.it/sport/lo_show_campioni_cosi_lippica_risponde_pista_accuse_ingiustificate/15-06-2010/articolo-id=453219-page=0-comments=1 |work=  |publisher= il Giornale |date= 2010-06-12 |accessdate= 2010-12-09 |archive-date= 2010-12-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101202133405/http://www.ilgiornale.it/sport/lo_show_campioni_cosi_lippica_risponde_pista_accuse_ingiustificate/15-06-2010/articolo-id=453219-page=0-comments=1 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。英國[[聖列治錦標|聖列治錦標]]技藝精湛雖然在四歲只曾勝出一場表列賽，但是從未失過取得獎金的機會。溫徹斯特曼克頓讓賽擊敗過美國著名草地馬匹[[建築大師_(馬)|建築大師]]<ref>{{cite news |first=Jack |last=Shinar |author= |coauthors= |title=Capella lands second Pride Stakes after year off |url=http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/57373/winchester-hits-target-in-manhattan-upset |work= |publisher=bloodhorse.com |date=2010-06-05 |accessdate=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309121558/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/57373/winchester-hits-target-in-manhattan-upset |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印族節日一直未能取勝，介乎於讓賽及分級賽之間浮沉，直到上場在土耳其勝出二級賽[[博斯普魯斯盃|博斯普魯斯盃]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Andrew |last= Scutts |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Indian Days leads British Group 1 raiding party |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=763943&argument=682674 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-09-04 |accessdate= 2010-12-07 }}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。好先生在今年勝除了遠征澳洲外，還勝出[[香港冠軍暨遮打盃|香港冠軍暨遮打盃]]。紅杉木則在加拿大的[[北地舞人草地錦標|北地舞人草地錦標]]中<ref>{{cite news |first= Patrick |last= Reed |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Redwood grinds out Northern Dancer Turf win |url= http://www.thoroughbredtimes.com/racing-news/2010/september/19/redwood-rides-rail-to-northern-dancer-victory.aspx |work=  |publisher= Thoroughbred Times |date= 2010-09-19 |accessdate= 2010-12-10 |archive-date= 2010-09-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100923161037/http://www.thoroughbredtimes.com/racing-news/2010/September/19/Redwood-rides-rail-to-Northern-Dancer-victory.aspx |dead-url= no }}</ref>輕勝。至勇威龍在[[香港經典盃|香港打吡預賽]]中擊敗過打吡冠軍極品絲綢。火龍駒在6月勝出第一班賽事，以後備馬匹補上。星光水晶受到傷患困擾，今年只角逐[[英國冠軍雌馬錦標|自豪錦標]]，結果以4個半馬位大勝對手而回<ref>{{cite news |first= Stuart |last= Riley |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Capella lands second Pride Stakes after year off |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=778453&argument=693126 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-10-16 |accessdate= 2010-12-07 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120913044931/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=778453&argument=693126 |archivedate= 2012-09-13 }}</ref>。董事會曾在三場一級賽中上名，當中包括2009年[[歌劇錦標|歌劇錦標]]亞軍。搖滾專輯在三歲的時候才在八月參與首場賽事，10月在加拿大勝出[[加拿大國際錦標|加拿大國際錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Jason |last= Shandler |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Canadian International: Joshua Tree Hangs On |url= http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/59381/canadian-international-joshua-tree-hangs-on |work=  |publisher= bloodhorse.com |date= 2010-10-16 |accessdate= 2010-12-07 |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115233/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/59381/canadian-international-joshua-tree-hangs-on |dead-url= no }}</ref>在賽日證實不良於行，被競賽董事勒令退出賽事。

