s/home.sd?story=773893&argument=741582|work=|publisher=racingpost.com|date=2010-10-01|accessdate=2010-12-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120912221524/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=773893&argument=741582|archivedate=2012-09-12}}</ref>，氣勢一時無兩。點心曾勝出09年主席短途獎。共創未來雖然在港只勝出一場賽事，但是前戰只輸給小橋流水些許。[[愛跑得|愛跑得]]以絕佳時間勝出精英碗<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=告達理開定期票愛跑得預賽贏得 ! |url=http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101025/rjnewa0001x0.html |work= |publisher=東方日報 |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120233527/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101025/rjnewa0001x0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以後備身份補上。[[繡球花_(馬)|繡球花]]原為[[星河大賽|星河大賽]]冠軍，但驗出禁藥被取消資格<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2010-12/news_2010120101623.html |title=「繡球花」體力足駱東尼有信心爭勝 |publisher=香港賽馬會 |accessdate=2009-12-08 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306205028/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2010-12%2Fnews_2010120101623.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

