小柏高今年第一場勝利是[[樂景傑錦標|樂景傑錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= James |last= Burn |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Capella lands second Pride Stakes after year off |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=716833&argument=685655 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-05-15 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120908090421/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=716833&argument=685655 |archivedate= 2012-09-08 }}</ref>，但之後再沒頭馬進帳，原因是四次遇上了歐洲馬王[[金剛威|金剛威]]，均未曾先於對手過終點。步步穩表現回勇，相隔三年再度勝出[[冠軍一哩賽|冠軍一哩賽]]<ref name="AbleOne VivaPataca"/>。友誼至上勝出[[董事盃_(香港)|董事盃]]<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=潘頓一級賽首W友誼至上 |url=http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20100201/rjnewa0002x0.html |work= |publisher=東方日報 |date=2010-02-01 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305020509/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20100201/rjnewa0002x0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上場比賽跑法失誤才大敗而回。締造美麗本年勝出[[香港經典一哩賽|香港經典一哩賽]]，亦在冠軍一哩賽跑第三。食夢精靈在[[女皇安妮錦標|女皇安妮錦標]]跑第三，上戰勝出一場膠沙地賽事。捷足先得上場以絕佳賽事爆冷勝出[[一哩冠軍賽|一哩冠軍賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first=  |last=  |author=  |coauthors=  |title= 13番人気エーシンフォワードがレコードVでマイル王襲名/マイルCS |url= http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=51629&category=A |work=  |publisher= netkeiba.com |date= 2010-11-21 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |archive-date= 2010-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101127012349/http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=51629&category=A |dead-url= no }}</ref>，以補充報名參加賽事。好爸爸是三屆香港一哩錦標冠軍<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=好爸爸歷史性三連霸 |url=http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20091214/rjnewa0004x0.html |work= |publisher=東方日報 |date=2009-12-14 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305070926/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20091214/rjnewa0004x0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但自香港金盃後就沒有好表現。勝眼光近期表現反覆，憑[[安田紀念賽|安田紀念賽]]跑第五而獲得參賽資格。自由好轉投方嘉柏後，確立了以一哩為中心的路線，在沙田錦標擊敗了負重磅的步步穩<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=自由好助都爾冧莊 |url=http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101025/rjnewa0002x0.html |work= |publisher=東方日報 |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-12-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304124730/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101025/rjnewa0002x0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。金獅威將勝出一班賽[[沙田一哩錦標|沙田一哩錦標]]外，在最近兩場分級賽均能上名。來自愛爾蘭的樂聖兩歲曾勝出[[杜何斯特錦標|杜何斯特錦標]]，在三歲亦勝出三級賽達士蒙錦標。庭園華座最好的成績是勝出二級賽[[韋士登錦標|韋士登錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= David |last= Baxter |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Royal Bench to the fore in Daniel Wildenstein |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=774384&argument=742644 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-10-03 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120911025017/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=774384&argument=742644 |archivedate= 2012-09-11 }}</ref>。驪勝名駒是兩場三級賽的盟主<ref>{{cite news |first= Desmond |last= Stoneham |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Rajsaman gives instant return for new owner |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=784008&argument=734508 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-10-31 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120907053454/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=784008&argument=734508 |archivedate= 2012-09-07 }}</ref>。莎貝寶駒連續兩屆勝出新市場舉行的[[太陽戰車錦標|太陽戰車錦標]]<ref>{{cite news |first= Stuart |last= Riley |author=  |coauthors=  |title= Sahpresa saunters to second Sun Chariot |url= http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=774300&argument=713063 |work=  |publisher= Racing Post |date= 2010-10-03 |accessdate= 2010-12-08 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://archive.is/20120907055346/http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=774300&argument=713063 |archivedate= 2012-09-07 }}</ref>，在角逐香港一哩錦標前被日本馬主吉田照哉買下。

