st Group 1 victory |url=http://www.racingpost.com/horses/home.sd?story=742035&argument=739872 |work= |publisher=Racing Post |date=2010-07-14 |accessdate=2010-12-09 }}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>，在凱旋門大賽犯規被取消資格。出道一度取得六連勝，今年亦勝出一級賽[[尚羅萬尼錦標|尚羅萬尼錦標]]的勝多利大。三歲雌馬有遠征加拿大獲得第一個一級賽冠軍的永勁<ref>{{cite news |first=John |last=Shadlern |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Reggane Rallies to Win E. P. Taylor |url=http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/59379/reggane-rallies-to-win-e-p-taylor |work= |publisher=bloodhorse.com |date=2010-10-16 |accessdate=2010-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212457/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/59379/reggane-rallies-to-win-e-p-taylor |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及連勝[[葉森橡樹大賽|葉森橡樹大賽]]及[[愛爾蘭橡樹大賽|愛爾蘭橡樹大賽]]的飛雪仙蹤<ref name="Snow Fairy"/>，其後勝出日本的[[伊丽莎白女王杯|伊丽莎白女王杯]]，成功取得巨額額外獎金<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=スノーフェアリー、外国馬史上初のV達成/エリザベス女王杯 |url=http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=51366&category=A |work= |publisher=netkeiba.com |date=2010-11-14 |accessdate=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2010-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101116050109/http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=51366&category=A |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

