大熱門是雌馬飛雪仙蹤，在開跑前仍獲得相當的支持，只得兩倍。起步後，包裝大師帶出，跟隨的是天鷹翱翔，熱門馬閒話一句、魔法幻影及飛雪仙蹤留後。在直路，由於慢步速的關係，包裝大師仍有餘勁，部份後上馬反應看似一般。但是留後的飛雪仙蹤克服了不利的形勢一直加速，在最後階段趕過帶出的魔法幻影勝出賽事，包裝大師結果跑第三而回。上屆冠軍萬千景象只得第四<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=飛雪仙蹤後上捧盃 |url=http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101213/rjnewa0003x0.html |work= |publisher=[[東方日報|東方日報]] |date=2010-12-13 |accessdate=2010-12-13 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010932/http://racing.on.cc/racing/new/20101213/rjnewa0003x0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Steve |last=Dennis |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Snow Fairy steals the show to lift the Cupe |url=http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/sha-tin-sha-tin-hong-kong-snow-fairy-steals-the-show-with-cup-win/798558/international/ |work= |publisher=Racing Post |date=2010-12-12 |accessdate=2010-12-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120908191424/http://www.racingpost.com/news/horse-racing/sha-tin-sha-tin-hong-kong-snow-fairy-steals-the-show-with-cup-win/798558/international/ |archivedate=2012-09-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2010-12%2Fnews_2010121201726.html |title=國泰航空香港盃騎師賽後評語 |accessdate=2021-01-23 |archive-date=2014-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123001547/http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2010-12%2Fnews_2010121201726.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

